{"tid":2097711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公司個廁所好奇怪！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-07-07T04:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T07:32:59.000Z","uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f64c8ba0116c9f90dd2b528797f03436395a079c","tid":2097711,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上星期已經試過一次,入到公司大廈廁所,聽到一收一放既水聲,十幾次.<br />\n我以為人地肚痛痾水,因為佢一放一下就有呻吟聲.<br />\n剛剛頭先我去廁所,見到有個高貴女人入黎,之後仲係度先照下鏡.<br />\n之後我入去方便,又聽到一收一放既水聲,十幾次,又係不停有呻吟聲.<br />\n之後我去洗手,個女人出黎,又唔似唔舒服.正正常常既樣.<br />\n其實我好想問下佢,你其實係咪肚痛,唔使發出咁大呻吟聲.<br />\n去大廈廁所聽到人唔唔去大大既聲就多,聽呻吟聲真係第一次.....</span></div></strong>"},{"pid":"1580462848392e235773b9d27d645aaab6048dcd","tid":2097711,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a6162ea1b9f8ebe5440e7777e56fb776a66c60","tid":2097711,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0b19727ea9a25ac96669b7eb06e2fbcacbaf23","tid":2097711,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"無是咁的0分"},{"pid":"c98d2ba589559e8ea4db394c9b170b802b6bee62","tid":2097711,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd0b19727ea9a25ac96669b7eb06e2fbcacbaf23","tid":2097711,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"無是咁的0分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">真事來架</div>"},{"pid":"5767253523359f2bf5c0473b16cba01af63ff61e","tid":2097711,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"5417